OL,3,CGladiator II trailer released 24 years
OL,4,Cafter original film
OL,6,FMore than 20 years after the original
OL,7,Fmovie was released and became a cult
OL,8,Fclassic, fans have been given a first
OL,9,Flook at Gladiator II.
OL,11,FIrish actor Paul Mescal faces off
OL,12,Fagainst Pedro Pascal in Sir Ridley
OL,13,FScott's highly-anticipated sequel to
OL,14,Fthe 2000 film that won several Oscars
OL,15,F- including Best Picture.
OL,17,FThe sequel is set several decades
OL,18,Fafter the events of the first movie.
