OL,3,CGladiator II trailer released 24 years
OL,4,Cafter original film
OL,6,FIt focuses on Lucius (Mescal), who was
OL,7,Fa child in the first film saved by
OL,8,FMaximus Decimus Meridius, played in
OL,9,Fthe original by Russell Crowe.
OL,11,FLucius was also the nephew of
OL,12,FCommodus, the first film's antagonist,
OL,13,Fplayed by Joaquin Phoenix.
OL,15,FAfter ending up in slavery following
OL,16,Fan invasion led by Roman general
OL,17,FMarcus Acacius played by Pedro Pascal,
OL,18,FLucius follows the inspiration of
OL,19,FMaximus and competes as a gladiator.
