OL,3,CGladiator II trailer released 24 years
OL,4,Cafter original film
OL,6,FThe sequel also features Denzel
OL,7,FWashington as Macrinus - a rich man of
OL,8,Finfluence who manages Lucius.
OL,10,FThe trailer includes clips from the
OL,11,Foriginal film, with Lucius referencing
OL,12,Fthe moment he saw Maximus defeat
OL,13,FCommodus.
OL,15,F"I remember that day. I never forgot
OL,16,Fit. That a slave could take revenge
OL,17,Fagainst an emperor", he says.
